X,Y,W,Z
X\otimes_{\pi}Y
S\in B(X,Z)
T\in B(Y,W)
S\otimes T\in B(X\otimes_{\pi} Y, Z\otimes_{\pi}W)
\|S\otimes T\|\leq \|S\|\cdot\|T\|
\epsilon > 0
x\in B_{X}
y\in B_{Y}
\|Sx\| > \|S\| - \epsilon\text{ and }\|Ty\| > \|T\| - \epsilon
\|S\otimes T(x\otimes y)\| > \|T\|\cdot \|S\| - \epsilon (\|S\| + \|T\|) + \epsilon
\epsilon\to 0
x\otimes y
X\otimes_{\pi} Y
\bf{\text{Available Fact}}
B_{X\otimes_{\pi} Y}
B_{X}\otimes B_{Y}
\Vert x\otimes y\Vert=\Vert x\Vert\Vert y\Vert\leq 1
\varepsilon\to 0
\Vert S\otimes T\Vert\geq \Vert S\Vert\Vert T\Vert
 \Vert S\otimes T\Vert \geq\Vert S\otimes T\Vert\Vert x\otimes y\Vert \geq\Vert(S\otimes T)(x\otimes y)\Vert =\Vert S(x)\otimes T(y)\Vert =\Vert S(x)\Vert\Vert T(y)\Vert \geq(\Vert S\Vert-\varepsilon)(\Vert T\Vert-\varepsilon) 
